# PeekDir

A Python utility to visualize directory structures with smart truncation of common file types.

## Installation
```bash
pip install PeekDir
```

## Usage
```bash
PeekDir [directory]
```

## Features
- Truncates file groups with >5 items
- Directory-first listing
- Permission handling
